      <title>Sidara 以风险上升为由终止 Wood Group 收购谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/sidara-ends-wood-group-takeover-talks-citing-rising-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工程公司 Sidara 表示不会对 John Wood Group Plc 提出明确收购要约，结束了长达数月的求购过程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/sidara-ends-wood-group-takeover-talks-citing-rising-risks</guid>
