    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔减持近一半股份后，苹果供应商股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/apple-supplier-stocks-slump-after-berkshire-nearly-halves-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 几乎减持了苹果公司一半的股份，导致苹果公司供应商的股价暴跌。周一，苹果公司股价下跌，而与此同时，市场普遍出现抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/apple-supplier-stocks-slump-after-berkshire-nearly-halves-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 06:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元升值加剧日本股市下跌，全球市场动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/intensifying-yen-rally-sinks-japan-stocks-rattles-global-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，日本金融市场动荡不安，日元兑美元汇率从 7 月低点反弹至约 13%，股市跌入熊市。日本基准政府债券收益率跌幅创 20 多年来最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/intensifying-yen-rally-sinks-japan-stocks-rattles-global-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股市暴跌加剧，纳斯达克期货下跌 5%：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美联储在支持放缓的经济方面行动太迟缓，全球股市抛售加剧，美国股指期货大幅下跌，导致投资者转向安全的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恐慌性抛售让亚洲股市迎来严峻的里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国经济进一步放缓以及日本股市持续暴跌，投资者风险偏好减弱，亚洲股市大幅下跌，而权重科技股的大幅抛售令情况更加糟糕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信心崩塌，日本股市跌入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者信心消失，日本东证股价指数从上月创下的历史高点下跌了 24%，日经 225 股票平均指数以日元计算出现最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:18:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
